        {
            "title": "川普警告:中國若向伊朗運送武器將面臨「大問題」",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/0HA1BlbgaBX0QoCVA5qaVQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEE2P0H6_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 美國總統唐納德·川普今日表示,如果中國向伊朗運送武器,將面臨「大問題」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普在白宮外對記者發表講話時,對伊朗外交和地區安全風險採取了複雜的態度,他表示與德黑蘭達成協議對他來說「沒有區別」,同時又將正在進行的接觸描述為「非常深入的談判」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普還指出波斯灣周邊的海軍活動加劇,稱掃雷艦正在作業並「清掃海峽」,並警告水中可能有「幾枚水雷」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在外交前景方面,川普補充說「也許他們會達成協議,也許不會」,同時表示「無論發生什麼,我們都會贏」。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d998b0e4-b5cf-3bbd-bb42-4c48302244ec-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國、伊朗和巴基斯坦之間的三方會談於週六開始,此前幾天宣布了一項脆弱的兩週停火協議,這場持續了七週的衝突已造成數千人死亡,並震撼了全球市場。這些討論是在美國和伊朗官員分別與巴基斯坦總理夏巴茲·謝里夫會晤之後進行的。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時,另一條外交軌道上的規劃也在進行中,以色列和黎巴嫩之間的談判預計將於下週在華盛頓特區舉行。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%8B%A5%E5%90%91%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E9%81%8B%E9%80%81%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8%E5%B0%87%E9%9D%A2%E8%87%A8-%E5%A4%A7%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C-220756273.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-12 06:17:33",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
